{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778900851692,"sessionID":"ses_1d1509c10ffedV5bHl2QpuEDMW","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-957dd6c4c13361ff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"## Summary of Changes\n- Removed `EC:1.4.3.22 {source=\"skos:broadMatch\"}` from `histamine oxidase activity` (GO:0052598), as it is already present as a broadMatch on its parent `diamine oxidase activity` (GO:0052597).\n- Changed the parent of `protein-lysine 6-oxidase activity` (GO:0004720) from `diamine oxidase activity` (GO:0052597) to `oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-NH2 group of donors, oxygen as acceptor` (GO:0016641).\n\n## Rationale\n- As requested in issue #31964, `histamine oxidase activity` should not have its own broadMatch to `EC:1.4.3.22` if the parent term already carries it.\n- `protein-lysine 6-oxidase activity` is not a diamine oxidase activity and should therefore be moved under the broader parent `GO:0016641`.\n\n## Validation\n- Performed `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl` procedure.\n- Ran `src/ontology/go-edit.obo-check` (via `make go-edit.obo-check`) which passed (empty output).\n","filePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778900851684,"end":1778900851690}},"id":"prt_e2ec04ce9001NclYcS5KLW4ucq","sessionID":"ses_1d1509c10ffedV5bHl2QpuEDMW","messageID":"msg_e2ec0175e001zGtVEXWNmzM4gz"}}
